	<text>
		<body>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Memphis&#44; Tenn.</placeName> <date>September 30 1863</date>.</p>
				<p>To the <addressee>Revd Isaac Leeser</addressee>.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)"><placeName>Philadelphia</placeName></p>
			<p rend="indent(2)"><placeName>Pa</placeName></p>
				<p>Dear Sir&#33;  Your favor came duly to hand and the<lb/> contents were duly noted&#44; I am already busy<lb/> to re&#45;write the manuscript and will after I have<lb/> done forward it to you&#44; I intend&#44; if you think<lb/> proper&#44; to publish a list in the back part of the book<lb/> of those who will subscribe for the work especially here in<lb/> <placeName>Memphis</placeName>&#44; where I am sanguine that I will be<lb/> able to defray the <sic>expences</sic> by their liberal subscription&#44;<lb/> perhaps you will be able to do the same in some<lb/> degree&#44; by calling attention to it in the Occident&#44;<lb/> the first part containing 8 chapters&#59; do you<lb/> think first to re&#45;write it all&#44; or to send it<lb/> as I am going along&#44; it will take me 3 or 4<lb/> weeks before I will be able to finish it.</p>
				<p>I believe I do owe you for 2 <add>Hebrew</add> for which<lb/> I will send you the money by the by.</p>
				<p>The members of our <add>Hebrew</add> want me to accept the office<lb/> of <add>Hebrew</add> <add>&#63;</add>  I do not know <sic>If</sic> I shall comply&#44;<lb/> the <persName>Revd Joel Alexander</persName> has given entire satisfactory<lb/> during the <add>Hebrew</add> especially his sermons&#44; as<lb/> I understood from reliable parties <persName>Dr S. Turka</persName><lb/> is not so much of <persName>Wise&#39;s</persName> school&#44; he is&#44; they<lb/> say&#44; more orthodox&#44; and does not advocate&#44;<lb/> reforms&#44; so mote is he&#33;</p>
				<p>With the manuscript I will try to send at<lb/> least &#36;200.00 which will enable you to commence<lb/> the work&#44; those who subscribe will have to pay<lb/> in advance&#44; I will write you shortly again</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">Yours very truly</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)"><persName role="author">Jacob J Peres</persName></p>
		</body>
	</text>
